column6: Help your friends\' and loved ones\' favorite movie stars come to them, by giving them the gift of entertainment - AMC Gift Cards! In the words of "Cousin Eddy" from "National Lampoon\'s Christmas Vacation:" "That\'s the gift that keeps on giving the whole year." AMC, the first in the exhibition industry to offer personalized gift cards, was also the first in the industry to launch circuit-wide gift cards in 2002. We think that\'s pretty cool too. Headquartered in Kansas City, Mo., AMC Entertainment Inc. is a leading theatrical exhibition and entertainment company. Promptly he renamed the location to "Cattle Baron Steak & Seafood Restaurant". Jeff operated this location for eight years before embarking on a successful expansion program. column6: "Natural Therapeutics Massage & Wellness is a locally owned and operated massage and wellness clinic in the heart of Colorado Springs, CO! We encourage our massage therapists to foster relationships with their clients and strive for a warm and inviting experience. We value our client's opinions and appreciate any and all feedback. We hope that you feel at home when you walk through our door! We believe that massage should be incorporated into your life at least once a month and offer affordable memberships to do just that! Our massage therapists believe in listening to your body and designing a treatment plan based on your individual needs. We encourage the use of therapeutic forms of massage and bodywork in hopes of relieving you from stressed, over worked and inflamed muscles! We believe massage therapy is a necessity and not a luxury and great way to increase your health and wellness. We also offer detoxifying treatments in our clinic to promote wellness. We encourage detoxifying the tissues and cells of the body in hopes of living a healthier and more energetic lifestyle! We also focus our clinic on the use of essential oils. We promote the use of oils in our massages and also offer information on how to incorporate them into your daily routine! Essential oils have very powerful and beneficial properties and can be used to maintain good health!"

column5: Daily Sonoma Wine Tours in the Heart of Sonoma Wine Country!', 'Enjoy Our Six-Hour Cable Car Wine Tour', 'Catered Picnic Lunch by the Girl & the Fig Restaurant', 'Entertaining facts and information about the area.'
column6: Join us on an exciting Sonoma wine tasting tour through historic Sonoma Valley aboard the “Original” Sonoma Wine Trolley! Built right from the blueprints, the Sonoma Wine Trolley is a motorized, authentic replica of a late 1890’s San Francisco cable car. The vintage, open-air design of the early California Street line offers a scenic view unmatched by any other touring vehicle. As you embark on a journey full of rich local history, you will meet fellow wine tasting enthusiasts, enjoy a Sonoma wine tasting tour at four unique Sonoma Valley Wineries, and learn what makes Sonoma Valley such a popular destination for wine lovers and foodies all over the world. One customer describes their experience by saying, “The settings were lovely and it was perfect to coast through the wine region in this open-air trolley. This is truly a fun way to spend the day… we only had 12 people on our trolley and by lunchtime we were all laughing and getting to know one another. This was a wonderful day that was orchestrated from start to finish by Sonoma Valley Wine Trolley Tours—thanks to all for giving us a day we will never forget.”'

We think that’s pretty cool too. Headquartered in Kansas City, Mo., AMC Entertainment Inc. is a leading theatrical exhibition and entertainment company. column6: "Rita’s Franchise Company, LLC, headquartered in Trevose, PA, is the largest Italian Ice concept in the nation with around 600 units operating in 31 states. Rita’s is continuing to grow nationally and internationally through franchise opportunities. The popular Rita's chain offers a variety of frozen treats including its famous Italian Ice, made fresh daily with real fruit, available in over 80 flavors, Old-Fashioned Frozen Custard, Milkshakes, Sundaes, Frozen Custard Cakes, Custard Cookie Sandwiches, layered Gelati, as well as its signature Misto, Blendini and Concrete creations. Since 1984, “Ice, Custard, Happiness” has been the brand’s motto, and for over 30 years Rita’s is still dedicated to serving up a big dose of happiness with our freshly made, delicious, custom treats, in a fun-filled atmosphere."

column6: Sit down to a meal the way Chicago intended it – big, bold, and jam-packed with the kind of flavor you only get from doing things right. At UNO’s, we make our dough fresh every day and let it rise for at least 24 hours. Our toppings are hand-chopped. The crust for each pizza is hand-stretched. And our craft brews are local and rotated often. Because we do it with craft, or not at all. See, back in 1943, we were the guys that went deep when the pizza world was still seeing nothing but flat. We made dough with a tall edge, topped with homemade sauce and more cheese than you could believe. That’s Chicago deep dish pizza, and we invented it. Our Chicago thin crust comes with a deep-dish attitude too. In fact, we have a whole menu of apps, entrées, and desserts so chalk-full of flavor we’ll have your taste buds screaming uncle. Craft is what we know – the same thing we’ve been serving ever since. We’re keeping the taps flowing and the pizza coming! At UNO’s, in craft we trust.'

column5: Located in Albuquerque, New Mexico', 'Come join in daily for the camaraderie, the good times and the spirit of Ireland.', "If you're looking for something different, something truly special, Two Fools Tavern is the place to be for cocktail hour, lunch time, dinner time or anytime."
column6: Two Fools Tavern is an unrelenting dream finally realized by folks who had a desire to bring a real Irish pub and eating establishment to Albuquerque, New Mexico. They envisioned and executed faithfully an authentic replication of the pubs they had visited in Ireland. The warmth, charm, European feel and essence is all evident in the Two Fools Tavern. The colors, furniture, pictures on the wall, the knick knacks placed throughout... and of course the ales, stouts and fine whiskies and cuisine of the Emerald Isle is all here to enjoy. The tavern invites everyone (of age) to come and visit, imbibe in a Guinness, artfully poured, and partake in your favorite Irish food.'

column5: Locations in Arizona, Colorado, Indiana, Maryland, Texas & DC.', 'EAT OUR FOOD, FEEL GOOD.'
column6: Modern Market serves real food. By real food, we mean food made from simple, whole ingredients. We serve food the way it was cooked hundreds of years ago - raw, grilled or cooked in a stone hearth oven. We avoid things like preservatives and artificial sweeteners and keep our ingredient lists short and sweet. We make things from scratch, which is a total pain, but it makes our food taste better. Our menu changes a lot. Sometimes it is because we grow tired of eating the same things, other times it is because different items come in season. Some of our items are locally sourced, some are organic and all are the highest quality we can find. We believe that a varied diet of simple, whole foods is what you should be eating everyday. So that is what we serve at Modern Market. When you eat these types of food, you feel better an hour later, not worse. There really are no "bad things" on our menu. We create great tasting foods that are good for you. Simple stuff.'

column6: Children’s Museum of Pittsburgh is a place that delights and inspires children, where they can take off on fantastic flights of imagination daily, and return to earth to ink a silkscreen in The Studio, build and tinker with old and new technologies in MAKESHOP, pump and move water in all directions in the new Waterplay, catch words that fall from the sky at “Text Rain” and much more. The Children’s Museum welcomes nearly 270, 000 visitors annually and provides tons of fun and loads of “real stuff” experiences for play and learning. Other interactive exhibit areas and experiences that inspire joy, creativity and curiosity include The Garage, Theater, Nursery, and Backyard. The Museum’s award-winning, three-story, center building is screened by a shimmering wind sculpture and connects two historic structures (Allegheny Post Office Building & the Buhl Building). In 2011 Children’s Museum of Pittsburgh was named as one of the nation’s ten top children’s museums by Parents magazine.'

column6: "Way back in 1990 when our founder, Charlie Zhang, opened the first Pick Up Stix(R), people came from miles around for his incredible House Special Chicken. There was just something about the succulent taste of tender chicken in a caramelized white wine sauce with garlic, soy and green onions wok'd fresh to order over a roaring fire.  They couldn't get enough of it. Well, Pick Up Stix has grown a lot since then and so has our menu. But folks are still addicted to our House Special Chicken. And our Orange Peel Chicken. And our Garlic Shrimp. And our Crispy Honey Chicken. And our Cream Cheese Wontons. And..... well you get the idea.  Come in to Pick Up Stix today and let us wok something fresh for you. Just be prepared to become addicted! column6: Help your friends\' and loved ones\' favorite movie stars come to them, by giving them the gift of entertainment - AMC Gift Cards! AMC Gift Cards are good for both movies and concessions and are reloadable at any theatre in the United States. Even better, AMC Gift Cards do not have any associated fees or expiration dates so your gift spans the test of time. In the words of "Cousin Eddy" from "National Lampoon\'s Christmas Vacation:" "That\'s the gift that keeps on giving the whole year." AMC, the first in the exhibition industry to offer personalized gift cards, was also the first in the industry to launch circuit-wide gift cards in 2002. We think that\'s pretty cool too. Headquartered in Kansas City, Mo., AMC Entertainment Inc. is a leading theatrical exhibition and entertainment company. With a history of industry leadership and innovation dating back to 1920, the company today serves hundreds of millions of guests annually through interests in 350 theatres with over 5,000 screens in four countries.'

column6: There’s no wishing upon a star, no fairy dust, no “Once upon a time” when it comes to how Dave and Cranky’s got its start. Like Genghis Khan, Dave (aka King Dave), sought to conquer and build an establishment where anyone could get great food, and a hefty dose of “tasteful abrasiveness”. After some searching he found himself a feisty Front of House and an Executive Chef with a wit that cracks like a whip *cue whip crack noise*. King David then founded Dave and Cranky’s with his spunky crew in Provo, Utah. And that’s all there is to tell here folks. So pound a can of red bull, listen to Limp Bizkit (wow am I that old?), speak with your pastor, and get your @*% in here.'

Apollo Beach, Florida', 'Fresh ingredients are the basis upon which all of our dishes are made', 'Local seafood is delivered straight to our restaurant directly from the docks.Imported seafood is flown in overnight fresh - NEVER frozen.', 'Our soups are made from scratch, some with over 50 ingredients.All salads are prepared to order and dressed with house-made dressings.Our sauces are scratch made-to-order - NEVER premade or bought.'
column6: "At Circles Waterfront Restaurant in Apollo Beach, we strive to provide all of our guests with an exceptional dining experience. Our experienced staff, relaxed marina setting, creative menu, and the freshest ingredients all combine to make our vision a reality. We pride ourselves on our exacting standards and uncompromising commitment to quality. Although we are aware that we don't always get everything 100% right, that's the goal we strive to meet everyday. Our belief that the best meals are created from the freshest ingredients is reflected in our kitchen. The one small freezer we own constitutes only 5% of our overall refrigerated food storage. For example, even our calamari is flown in fresh - not frozen, and we receive it whole - not cut. We hand-cut each piece, dip it into our original house-made batter which is prepared daily from scratch, and then hand-fry it in single made-to-order batches. In addition, we have a 72-hour turn over on our entire food inventory, which means that nothing, from seafood to salad ingredients, is ever in our pantry for more than three days. This type of turn over is unheard of in our segment of the restaurant industry. The choices we make on food selection, storage, and preparation are unparalleled in our area and we believe they are paramount in creating truly great food."

column5: Located in Tacoma, WA', 'Chef/owner Gordon Naccarato—a former winner of Food & Wine’s coveted TOP TEN BEST NEW CHEFS in America', 'The menu is extensive and features everything from fresh shucked local oysters and raw Beef Carpaccio to delicious Tacos and locally smoked Steelhead and includes many Vegan and gluten-free options', 'Pacific Grill is Tacoma’s most Award-Winning restaurant.'
column6: Pacific Grill is Tacoma’s most Award-Winning restaurant. A stunning urban space, at home in any major city that is perfect for romance, great conversation and world-class food. Chef/owner Gordon Naccarato—a former winner of Food & Wine’s coveted TOP TEN BEST NEW CHEFS in America—describes his food as fun dining-not fine dining with dishes perfect for sharing with a group of friends, entertaining business clients or celebrating your special occasion. The menu is extensive and features everything from fresh shucked local oysters and raw Beef Carpaccio to delicious Tacos and locally smoked Steelhead and includes many Vegan and gluten-free options. For smaller appetites, many of the menu items such as Angry Pasta with Prawns or Classic Clam Linguine can be served as half-portions. Order a Chopped Wedge Salad and get the bone-in New York Steak all for yourself, or share tapas-style and try many appetizers like the famous BLT Salad with the world’s best bacon. And don’t miss their Pastry Chef’s decadent desserts. The Bar area is packed with guests enjoying Tacoma’s Best Happy Hour as voted by our guests—even beating out our restaurant friends to the north in Seattle. Located in the gorgeously restored historic Waddell Building in the heart of downtown.'

column5: 6 elegant holders ideal for a presenting gift cards to friends, family or co-workers; gift card holders measure 3-1/4 x 4-3/4 Inches', 'Inside slot to hold gift card creates a clever pop-up effect; each holder has a blank area inside for personalization', 'Package includes 6 color-coordinated envelopes; gift cards holders are USPS approved for mailing; no extra postage required', 'Jillson Roberts gift card holders are available in a vast array of fun and fashionable designs perfect for any occasion; all gift card holders are made in the USA', 'Jillson Roberts also offers a beautiful selection of environmentally sensitive gift wrap, wine and gift bags, tissue, ribbon, Tyvek designer mailers and more, available on Amazon'
column6: "Birthdays, weddings, baby showers, anniversaries, graduation … so many special occasions and so many gift-giving dilemmas. What size? What color? How many? What if they already have one? Thank goodness for gift cards! And Jillson Roberts gift card holders are the perfect way to present a gift card because they're really like a greeting card and gift wrap all in one. The holders measure 3-1/4 x 4-3/4 Inches; an inside slot to hold a gift card creates a wonderful pop-up effect and there's even a blank area for writing a personalized note. They come with color-coordinated envelopes and are USPS approved for mailing with no additional postage required. Wow, doesn't get much easier than that! The gift card holders are designed to happily mix and match with Jillson Roberts gift wraps, tissues, wine and bottle bags, ribbons, raffia, crinkle shred and colorful Tyvek padded mailers to let your unique special occasion style shine. Jillson Roberts is proud to offer the largest, most comprehensive presentation of eclectic and environmentally sensitive paper products available on the market today; proof that one can, indeed, give beautifully and responsibly. They invite you to explore their fresh and innovative collections available on Amazon."

Apollo Beach, Florida', 'Fresh ingredients are the basis upon which all of our dishes are made', 'Local seafood is delivered straight to our restaurant directly from the docks.Imported seafood is flown in overnight fresh - NEVER frozen.', 'Our soups are made from scratch, some with over 50 ingredients.All salads are prepared to order and dressed with house-made dressings.Our sauces are scratch made-to-order - NEVER premade or bought.'
column6: "At Circles Waterfront Restaurant in Apollo Beach, we strive to provide all of our guests with an exceptional dining experience. Our experienced staff, relaxed marina setting, creative menu, and the freshest ingredients all combine to make our vision a reality. We pride ourselves on our exacting standards and uncompromising commitment to quality. Although we are aware that we don't always get everything 100% right, that's the goal we strive to meet everyday. Our belief that the best meals are created from the freshest ingredients is reflected in our kitchen. The one small freezer we own constitutes only 5% of our overall refrigerated food storage. For example, even our calamari is flown in fresh - not frozen, and we receive it whole - not cut. We hand-cut each piece, dip it into our original house-made batter which is prepared daily from scratch, and then hand-fry it in single made-to-order batches. In addition, we have a 72-hour turn over on our entire food inventory, which means that nothing, from seafood to salad ingredients, is ever in our pantry for more than three days. This type of turn over is unheard of in our segment of the restaurant industry. The choices we make on food selection, storage, and preparation are unparalleled in our area and we believe they are paramount in creating truly great food."

column5: Located in Tacoma, WA', 'Chef/owner Gordon Naccarato—a former winner of Food & Wine’s coveted TOP TEN BEST NEW CHEFS in America', 'The menu is extensive and features everything from fresh shucked local oysters and raw Beef Carpaccio to delicious Tacos and locally smoked Steelhead and includes many Vegan and gluten-free options', 'Pacific Grill is Tacoma’s most Award-Winning restaurant.'
column6: Pacific Grill is Tacoma’s most Award-Winning restaurant. A stunning urban space, at home in any major city that is perfect for romance, great conversation and world-class food. Chef/owner Gordon Naccarato—a former winner of Food & Wine’s coveted TOP TEN BEST NEW CHEFS in America—describes his food as fun dining-not fine dining with dishes perfect for sharing with a group of friends, entertaining business clients or celebrating your special occasion. The menu is extensive and features everything from fresh shucked local oysters and raw Beef Carpaccio to delicious Tacos and locally smoked Steelhead and includes many Vegan and gluten-free options. For smaller appetites, many of the menu items such as Angry Pasta with Prawns or Classic Clam Linguine can be served as half-portions. Order a Chopped Wedge Salad and get the bone-in New York Steak all for yourself, or share tapas-style and try many appetizers like the famous BLT Salad with the world’s best bacon. And don’t miss their Pastry Chef’s decadent desserts. The Bar area is packed with guests enjoying Tacoma’s Best Happy Hour as voted by our guests—even beating out our restaurant friends to the north in Seattle. Located in the gorgeously restored historic Waddell Building in the heart of downtown.'

column5: 6 elegant holders ideal for a presenting gift cards to friends, family or co-workers; gift card holders measure 3-1/4 x 4-3/4 Inches', 'Inside slot to hold gift card creates a clever pop-up effect; each holder has a blank area inside for personalization', 'Package includes 6 color-coordinated envelopes; gift cards holders are USPS approved for mailing; no extra postage required', 'Jillson Roberts gift card holders are available in a vast array of fun and fashionable designs perfect for any occasion; all gift card holders are made in the USA', 'Jillson Roberts also offers a beautiful selection of environmentally sensitive gift wrap, wine and gift bags, tissue, ribbon, Tyvek designer mailers and more, available on Amazon'
column6: "Birthdays, weddings, baby showers, anniversaries, graduation … so many special occasions and so many gift-giving dilemmas. What size? What color? How many? What if they already have one? Thank goodness for gift cards! And Jillson Roberts gift card holders are the perfect way to present a gift card because they're really like a greeting card and gift wrap all in one. The holders measure 3-1/4 x 4-3/4 Inches; an inside slot to hold a gift card creates a wonderful pop-up effect and there's even a blank area for writing a personalized note. They come with color-coordinated envelopes and are USPS approved for mailing with no additional postage required. Wow, doesn't get much easier than that! The gift card holders are designed to happily mix and match with Jillson Roberts gift wraps, tissues, wine and bottle bags, ribbons, raffia, crinkle shred and colorful Tyvek padded mailers to let your unique special occasion style shine. Jillson Roberts is proud to offer the largest, most comprehensive presentation of eclectic and environmentally sensitive paper products available on the market today; proof that one can, indeed, give beautifully and responsibly. They invite you to explore their fresh and innovative collections available on Amazon."
